data.description: Own a beautiful 2-story home with 5-bedrooms and 2-1/2 baths with primary bedroom downstairs. It includes many upgrades including energy-efficient appliances, granite countertops in kitchen and bathrooms, designer wood cabinets, brushed nickel hardware and an attached two-car garage. An open layout with a master suite downstairs complete with walk-in closet, a spacious game room upstairs, as well as a fully fenced backyard. Walking distance to elementary school and community recreational areas. One of the Best Priced homes in the neighborhood!!
